{"tid":1962422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】巴西教育部長指中國圖藉疫情支配世界","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:33:33.000Z","uid":70063,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edb20428cd8ce9e8da745cff5c794f421677dc6c","tid":1962422,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"巴西右翼政府一名官員指中國醫療設備生產商發瘟疫財，並指武漢肺炎疫情與中國「圖謀支配世界」有關，再次激怒中方。<br />\n<br />\n教育部長魏因特勞布（Abraham Weintraub）上周六在Twitter發文說：「從地緣政治角度看，誰會在這場波及全球的危機後變得更強？巴西有誰人與這個無懈可擊的支配世界計劃扯上關係？」<br />\n魏因特勞布在他的葡文推文中，特地將「Brazil」串成「BLazil」，籍一位有口吃的卡通人物，諷刺中國人的「懶音」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然推文周日已經刪除，但已觸動中方神經。中國駐巴西大使館指推文荒謬卑鄙，非常之種族歧視。大使楊萬明要求巴西解釋。不過，魏因特勞布堅持推文無問題，呼籲中國做多些事情幫助抗疫。他說：「如果中國向我們出售1,000部呼吸機，我會在大使館前跪地道歉兼自認白癡。」<br />\n<br />\n中國是巴西最大貿易夥伴，而巴西在拉丁美洲國家中疫情最嚴重，1.1萬宗確診，逾500人死。衞生部長曼德塔（Luiz Henrique Mandetta）上周說，巴西向中國訂購呼吸機及其他醫療物資困難重重，指部份訂單遭無故取消。事件引起網民熱烈討論，「TradeBlockadeOnChinaNow」（即時貿易制裁中國）主題成為巴西Twitter頭號熱門話題。<br />\n<br />\n疫情爆發後，中巴關係越趨緊張，總統博爾索納羅兒子、眾議員愛德華多（Eduardo Bolsonaro）上月的惹火推文，尤其起催化作用。他批評中國獨裁政權隱瞞疫情，猶如前蘇聯隱瞞切爾諾貝爾核災，上周又「仿傚」其父的偶像、美國總統特朗普，使用中國最不喜歡的字眼「中國病毒」形容導致武肺的新形冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐里約熱內盧總領事李揚在當地報章撰文反擊愛德華多的「辱華言論」，指愛德華「幼稚無知」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200407/CDDXPUHGTHSGDFQJ2NKX2MU644/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0IQjp2CFqIA-rYPPqGUIspBMFTsyckb9xm6UxeSxutN42yzQEe3gsl_FA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200407%2FCDDXPUHGTHSGDFQJ2NKX2MU644%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0IQjp2CFqIA-rYPPqGUIspBMFTsyckb9xm6UxeSxutN42yzQEe3gsl_FA&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=2ea33cd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200407%2FCDDXPUHGTHSGDFQJ2NKX2MU644%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0IQjp2CFqIA-rYPPqGUIspBMFTsyckb9xm6UxeSxutN42yzQEe3gsl_FA&h=77234975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200407/CDDXPUHGTHSGDFQJ2NKX2MU644/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0IQjp2CFqIA-rYPPqGUIspBMFTsyckb9xm6UxeSxutN42yzQEe3gsl_FA</a>"},{"pid":"bd0ac9b0c29a8939d4ee60d58e5d4d5d3c9de938","tid":1962422,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81238b852647c552d137e575eb5777ad49d15db4","tid":1962422,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb0ad28628c0b4d6f10105c2e36d2631ff6bd11","tid":1962422,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n根本細菌戰<br />\n其他國家借機清咁啲鬼先<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a9a750de70d5da200f6a5ff6df99c79f3d3d99e9","tid":1962422,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"個個都出post, 有媒體報導就話delete咗 sry sry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都屌柒中国玩彈出彈入"},{"pid":"2a2bbed44568cda032d7986006eb3b8f03838c83","tid":1962422,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113ee5983be4def